The paper deals with image retrieval, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of texture descriptors and distance criteria suggests that the paper may also belong to the subcategories of multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the use of predefined pattern units may indicate the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in the proposed method.
